          "settings": {
            "question": "Promotion Details",
            "answer": "<p>Discounts are applied as instant price reductions on selected products during the campaign period. Savings vary by product type and currency (USD), as outlined below.</p><p>Single Products</p><ul><li>Yarbo Lawn Mower: Save $600 USD</li><li>Yarbo Lawn Mower Pro: Save $300 USD</li></ul><p>Bundles</p><ul><li>Yarbo Lawn Mower + Snow Blower + Blower Bundles: Save $700 USD</li><li>Yarbo Lawn Mower + Snow Blower: Save $700 USD</li><li>Yarbo Lawn Mower + Blower: Save $700 USD</li><li>Yarbo Lawn Mower Pro + Snow Blower + Blower: Save $400 USD</li><li>Yarbo Lawn Mower Pro + Snow Blower: Save $400 USD</li><li>Yarbo Lawn Mower Pro + Blower: Save $400 USD</li></ul><p>Other bundles are not included in this promotion.</p><p>Modules</p><ul><li>Lawn Mower Module: Save $200 USD</li><li>Lawn Mower Pro Module: Save $200 USD </li></ul><p>Additional coupons or promotional offers may be combined with base discounts where applicable. Final savings and eligibility are subject to the rules displayed on the product page at checkout.</p>"
          }
        },
        "category_mAVWtg": {
          "type": "category",
          "settings": {
            "title": "COVERAGE & ELIGIBILITY",
            "bg_color": "#e5e5e5"
          }
        },
        "faq_QdbYwk": {
          "type": "faq",
          "settings": {
            "question": "Refunds & Returns",
            "answer": "<ul><li>Yarbo offers a <strong>30-day return window</strong> starting from the earlier of either product activation or three days after delivery.</li><li>Items must be returned in <strong>original packaging</strong>, with all accessories included, and in <strong>resalable condition</strong>.</li><li>Missing packaging or accessories may result in a <strong>deduction from the refund</strong>.</li><li>For more details, please refer to the official return policy on the Yarbo website.<br/></li></ul>"
          }
        },
        "faq_JYc3H4": {
          "type": "faq",
          "settings": {
            "question": "Shipping",
            "answer": "<ul><li>Orders are typically delivered within <strong>3–8 business days</strong>.</li></ul>"
